{"tid":1931791,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［又贏］日本一名故意到酒吧播毒的確診男子死亡","createTime":"2020-03-18T10:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T12:00:32.000Z","uid":88491,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"93abc3df2541a47bb7eab285e061b0f3a374e6fd","tid":1931791,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:39:37.000Z","msg":"日本一名確診新型肺炎後，故意到酒吧散播病毒的男子，延至今日死亡。死者是一名住是愛知縣的57歲男子，今個月4日被檢測對新型冠狀病毒呈陽性，但他無視當局指示，當日傍晚仍然前往當地一間酒吧，並向家人透露是故意外出散播病毒，翌日入院治療，延至今日不治。涉事酒吧事後已經暫停營業，一名30多歲的女職員上星期四亦確診，酒吧以妨礙業務為由追討賠償。日本目前有超過1500人確診新型肺炎，包括鑽石公主號郵輪的乘客及船員，死亡病例有36宗。<br />\n<br />\n2020-03-18 18:34:15<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n崇日能又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />✌🏻"},{"pid":"78de3420172653a12f08557fcb24a3a2294abfa2","tid":1931791,"uid":43061,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:39:58.000Z","msg":"勇武過香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038d109b4565175dcb84b1229dd141f0e5f1492e","tid":1931791,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:40:06.000Z","msg":"崇日𠃊rip"},{"pid":"bd71e1f99ee0dc282a407b5bbe975a408f54f126","tid":1931791,"uid":203454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:41:02.000Z","msg":"韓國人真係好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係我哋日本人高質啲🤙"},{"pid":"5c1ad5c03a62a336841c6bde74308a85159f0e14","tid":1931791,"uid":101481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:42:47.000Z","msg":"追討邊個"},{"pid":"cb56be28bca18ed67eea3f1a2af936fb6e96741e","tid":1931791,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"78de3420172653a12f08557fcb24a3a2294abfa2","tid":1931791,"uid":43061,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:39:58.000Z","msg":"勇武過香港人<img src=\"/a